e><blockquote>我砌過好多部機，都有幾部有依個問題，但之後係清完bios就正常用到，試下清bios啦</blockquote><br />\n清bios係點解?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我太蠢唔係太知</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-9RnIj-EcdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-9RnIj-EcdQ&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5caa791c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-9RnIj-EcdQ</a></blockquote><br />\n認真，試試佢</blockquote><br />\n咪老點人啦，你睇睇rx470個spec有冇analog out先啦"},{"pid":"41b3fa3f4846d5ee895b22ca83734983f36ffb71","tid":123752,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"砌完機之後,你只要有裝顯示卡,你個mon就一定要駁顯示卡<br />\n岩岩裝完機梗係冇driver啦,但係顯示卡一樣識得出畫面俾你架<br />\n你裝顯示卡driver係俾佢用顯示卡OpenGL, DirectX呢D功能"},{"pid":"cd475b379445401adc193f099cc17781c5beb9fb","tid":123752,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我砌過好多部機，都有幾部有依個問題，但之後係清完bios就正常用到，試下清bios啦</blockquote><br />\n清bios係點解?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我太蠢唔係太知</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-9RnIj-EcdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-9RnIj-EcdQ&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5caa791c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-9RnIj-EcdQ</a></blockquote><br />\n認真，試試佢</blockquote><br />\n咪老點人啦，你<span style=\"color: red;\">睇睇rx470個spec有冇analog out先啦</span></blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"ca6a7434ee419775476223c6d789977725b7f83b","tid":123752,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"開唔到機一定係以下問題<br />\n<br />\n利申: 十幾年砌機經驗<br />\n<br />\nCPU <br />\n- 睇下針腳有無曲到, 通常有時柒下柒下會調轉咗塊版就收得皮<br />\n- 插4針 SPEAKER, 睇下有無debug 聲CHECK下咩問題<br />\n- 睇下有無唔好彩爆CAP<br />\n- CLEAR 下BIOS<br />\n<br />\nRAM <br />\n- 幾多條RAM, 要跟番佢個次序插<br />\n- 可以先試插一條<br />\n<br />\nVGA <br />\n- 要插PCI-E 供電 (睇卡, 通常1070 以上有二個)<br />\n- 試下插第二個PCI-E 插座<br />\n<br />\nPOWER-SUPPLY<br />\n- 8 pin power 要插<br />\n- 睇下底版啲燈正唔正常"},{"pid":"1015cb89c14fa07ee8d78d03cd72c8982a20b8cd","tid":123752,"uid":61071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你張display 卡有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係要換moon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 暫時用住內顯先 <br />\n呢排都好忙未有時間打機住<br />\n遲下先再買converter/moon啦唯有"},{"pid":"7d3a85a61d711d1b47131bb35ed70057e71b3a4d","tid":123752,"uid":61071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你張display 卡有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係要換moon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,都話清清bios就得，我幾部機都係咁</blockquote><br />\n依家唔係講緊rx470唔support就咁用果舊adapter轉vga咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係買舊converter 一係換moon</blockquote><br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da59d137a9798f9d48601bb3786b3f3bec4cda6","tid":123752,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你張display 卡有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係要換moon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 暫時用住內顯先 <br />\n呢排都好忙未有時間打機住<br />\n遲下先再買converter/moon啦唯有</blockquote><br />\nconverter 應該都要舊幾水 (唔知共狗國會唔會平d)<br />\n三舊水執隻二手moon頂住先可能抵玩d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9103efb14044d9049859d6beb9778acfa221c6cb","tid":123752,"uid":61071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你張display 卡有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係要換moon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 暫時用住內顯先 <br />\n呢排都好忙未有時間打機住<br />\n遲下先再買converter/moon啦唯有</blockquote><br />\nconverter 應該都要舊幾水 (唔知共狗國會唔會平d)<br />\n三舊水執隻二手moon頂住先可能抵玩d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪有供電+audio output 既就係converter可以轉?"},{"pid":"a849294f7382199ace0e804e95c743d272baaf68","tid":123752,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁你張display 卡有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係要換moon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 暫時用住內顯先 <br />\n呢排都好忙未有時間打機住<br />\n遲下先再買converter/moon啦唯有</blockquote><br />\nconverter 應該都要舊幾水 (唔知共狗國會唔會平d)<br />\n三舊水執隻二手moon頂住先可能抵玩d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪有供電+audio output 既就係converter可以轉?</blockquote><br />\n我check返原來仲有隻active adapter (入面有晶片) 都可以做到，即係話如果你手上果隻係既話都可以，但如果係passive就唔得 ( passive 好似都有audio out )<br />\n你可以check check先, hdmi轉vga我冇機會用唔confirm <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e0a54553132d5854a453cf8da277fa4f02228d","tid":123752,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"我以前見到既類似係咁，呢種就一定冇死<br />\n<img src=\"https://sgcdn.startech.com/005329/media/products/main/HD2VGAMMX.main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsgcdn.startech.com%2F005329%2Fmedia%2Fproducts%2Fmain%2FHD2VGAMMX.main.jpg&h=b3d954a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a51165fbc80892459519ea4ade9cc4641d11fd5","tid":123752,"uid":61071,"like":0,"dislike"